      <title>油价暴跌后，OPEC+ 同意暂停增加石油供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/opec-has-deal-to-pause-planned-oil-hike-for-2-months-delegate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求脆弱导致油价暴跌，OPEC+达成协议，暂停原定的石油增产两个月。]]></description>
